__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT pe.id as event, 
    fq1.name as q1_name, 
    rn.fixed_value as value, 
    rn.fixed_units as units, 
    fq2.name as q2_name, 
    rd.fixed_value as date
FROM far_production_events as pe
    inner join far_responses_numeric as rn on rn.event = pe.id
    inner join far_responses_date as rd on rd.event = pe.id
    inner join frm_questions as fq1 on rn.question = fq1.id
    inner join frm_questions as fq2 on rd.question = fq2.id
